      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/grace-lavender/" target="_blank">Grace</a>,
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/daniel-ramiro-lanz/" target="_blank">Dani</a>
      and <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/felipe-fischel/" target="_blank">Felipe</a>.
    </div>
  </ul>

</div>
